<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <title>About Us - EEG Energy Services Limited</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main class="container my-5 about-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section text-center">
      <h1>We Are EEG Energy Services Limited</h1>
      <p>Providing unmatched expertise in calibration and instrumentation services.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <div class="container my-5 about-page" id="about">
      <h2 class="text-center">About <span class="text-red">EEG</span></h2>
      <div class="row">
        <!-- Left Section -->
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>
            EEG Energy Serices Limited is a subsidiary of Wellfliud Services Limited, established with the aim of delivering 
            premium quality calibration and instrumentation services to various industries, including Oil & Gas, Energy, and Manufacturing. 
            With a commitment to precision and customer satisfaction, our services are tailored to meet industry standards and 
            ensure operational excellence for our clients.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our state-of-the-art facilities, coupled with a team of highly skilled professionals, enable us to offer comprehensive 
            solutions for calibration, instrumentation rentals, and asset management. We are positioned to provide exceptional support 
            both onshore and offshore, ensuring reliability and efficiency in every service we deliver.
          </p>
          <p>
            From inception, our mission has been to provide excellence in all aspects of calibration and instrumentation services. 
            We take pride in fostering long-term partnerships with our clients and stakeholders, ensuring a positive impact across the industries we serve.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Section -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="bg-light p-3 rounded">
            <h4>Quick Links</h4>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/services">Our Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
              <li><a href="/#get-quote">Request a Quote</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-light p-3 rounded mt-3">
            <h4>Downloads</h4>
            <a href="/brochure.pdf" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">Download Brochure</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission and Vision Section -->
    <div class="container my-5" id="mission-vision">
      <h2 class="text-center">Our <span class="text-red">Mission</span> & <span class="text-red">Vision</span></h2>
      <div class="about-page">
        <div class="card-container">
          <div class="card">
            <img src="images/mission-statement.png" alt="Mission Icon" class="card-icon">
            <h4>MISSION STATMENT</h4>
            <p>To continuously search for technology and train personnel to enhance quality service delivery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <img src="/images/business-vision.png" alt="Vision Icon" class="card-icon">
            <h4>VISION STATEMENT</h4>
            <p>To become a sought-after quality assurance company in the African Continent and beyond.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
